@startuml
title Student Quiz Attempt - Sequence Diagram
autonumber

actor Student
participant StudentController
participant SessionService
participant StudentQuizServiceImpl as StudentQuizService
participant StudentRepository
participant QuizRepository
participant QuizAttemptRepository
participant QuizScoringStrategy as ScoringStrategy

Student -> StudentController: GET /student/home
StudentController -> SessionService: requireRole(session, STUDENT)
SessionService --> StudentController: SessionUser
StudentController -> StudentQuizService: getAvailableQuizzes(studentId)
StudentQuizService -> StudentRepository: findById(studentId)
StudentRepository --> StudentQuizService: Student
StudentQuizService -> QuizRepository: findBySectionAndCourseOrderByAvailableFromDesc(section, course)
QuizRepository --> StudentQuizService: List<Quiz>
loop for each quiz
  StudentQuizService -> QuizAttemptRepository: findByQuizAndStudent(quiz, student)
  QuizAttemptRepository --> StudentQuizService: Optional<QuizAttempt>
  StudentQuizService -> QuizAttemptRepository: existsByQuizAndStudent(quiz, student)
  QuizAttemptRepository --> StudentQuizService: boolean
end
StudentQuizService --> StudentController: List<QuizCardView>
StudentController --> Student: Render dashboard

Student -> StudentController: GET /student/quiz/{quizId}
StudentController -> SessionService: requireRole(session, STUDENT)
SessionService --> StudentController: SessionUser
StudentController -> StudentQuizService: getQuizForAttempt(studentId, quizId)
StudentQuizService -> StudentRepository: findById(studentId)
StudentQuizService -> QuizRepository: findById(quizId)
StudentQuizService -> QuizAttemptRepository: existsByQuizAndStudent(quiz, student)
StudentQuizService --> StudentController: QuizAttemptView
StudentController --> Student: Render attempt page

Student -> StudentController: POST /student/quiz/{quizId}/submit
StudentController -> SessionService: requireRole(session, STUDENT)
SessionService --> StudentController: SessionUser
StudentController -> StudentQuizService: submitQuiz(studentId, quizId, answers)
StudentQuizService -> StudentRepository: findById(studentId)
StudentQuizService -> QuizRepository: findById(quizId)
StudentQuizService -> QuizAttemptRepository: existsByQuizAndStudent(quiz, student)
StudentQuizService -> ScoringStrategy: score(quiz, selectedOptions)
ScoringStrategy --> StudentQuizService: ScoringResult
StudentQuizService -> QuizAttemptRepository: save(quizAttempt)
QuizAttemptRepository --> StudentQuizService: QuizAttempt
StudentQuizService --> StudentController: QuizSubmissionResultView
StudentController --> Student: Show immediate score
@enduml
